fields.label: Testimonials
fields.name: cpt_testimonials
fields.instructions: Turn off to disable the Testimonials Post Type.

fields.label: Testimonials Name
fields.name: cpt_testimonials_name
fields.instructions: Overwrites the default 'Testimonials' post-type name with content of this field. If this is not updating on the front-end, you may have to refresh the permalinks via Settings > Permalinks.

fields.label: Default Logo
fields.name: default_logo
fields.instructions: Select an image file for your logo.

fields.label: Mobile Logo
fields.name: mobile_logo
fields.instructions: Select an image file for your mobile logo.

sub_fields.label: Show Nav
sub_fields.name: show_nav
sub_fields.instructions: Select the breakpoint where the nav menu will show in header.  Any breakpoint below the selected will display the mobile menu/hamburger.

sub_fields.label: Header Position
sub_fields.name: header_position
sub_fields.instructions: Controls the position of the header to be in the top, left or right of the site. The main menu height, header padding and logo margin options will auto adjust based off your selection for ideal aesthetics.

sub_fields.label: 100% Header Width
sub_fields.name: header_width
sub_fields.instructions: Turn on to have the inner header contents display at 100% width according to the window size. Turn off to follow fixed container width.

sub_fields.label: Logo Height
sub_fields.name: logo_height
sub_fields.instructions: Set the max height for the logo in the header.

sub_fields.label: Sticky Header
sub_fields.name: sticky_header
sub_fields.instructions: Turn on to enable a sticky header.

sub_fields.label: Position
sub_fields.name: sticky_header_position
sub_fields.instructions: Sticky Top pushes the site down the height of the header, Fixed top overlays the header on top of the site.

sub_fields.label: Logo Height
sub_fields.name: sticky_logo_height
sub_fields.instructions: Set the max height for the logo in the sticky header.

sub_fields.label: Predefined Theme Skin
sub_fields.name: sticky_theme
sub_fields.instructions: Controls the main theme skin to be light or dark. Select a skin and all color options will change to the defined selection.

sub_fields.label: Page Title Bar
sub_fields.name: page_title_bar
sub_fields.instructions: Controls how the page title bar displays.

sub_fields.label: 100% Title Bar Width
sub_fields.name: title_bar_width
sub_fields.instructions: Turn on to have the inner title bar contents display at 100% width according to the window size. Turn off to follow fixed container width.
